title: OCS fantasy bracket day 1 over!
body:

Are you on track to earn the 10 win IP boost and Arclight Vel'koz? http://on.fb.me/1BwdoLg

I may check it out at the time, if my downloads are done. But Aussie speed so awful it'll be June before this download is done.
